item.title: Guzman y Gomez Shares Plunge as Sales Growth Slows in Australia
item.description: Shares of Guzman y Gomez Ltd. tumbled by the most since its Sydney listing last year after the Mexican-themed fast-food chain flagged a sales slowdown in its Australian restaurants.
